TC01.Measure: Partial Cell Availability (node restarts excluded) for NB-IoT
TC01.SQL: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50) =DATETIME_VALUE, @MOID varchar(200)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE, @SN varchar(200)=NODE_NAME_VALUE select CAST(ROUND(avg(KPI_Value), 2) AS NUMERIC(36,2)) AS kpiValue from (SELECT DATETIME_ID, 100*((900*(15/15))-(SUM(PMCELLDOWNTIMEAUTO)+SUM(PMCELLDOWNTIMEMAN)))/(900*(15/15)) AS KPI_Value FROM DC_E_ERBS_NBIOTCELL_RAW where DATETIME_ID = @DATETIME_ID  AND MOID=@MOID AND  SN=@SN GROUP BY DATETIME_ID ORDER BY DATETIME_ID ASC) A

TC02.SQL: DECLARE @DATETIME_ID varchar(50) =DATETIME_VALUE, @MOID varchar(200)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE, @SN varchar(200)=NODE_NAME_VALUE select CAST(ROUND(avg(KPI_Value), 2) AS NUMERIC(36,2)) AS kpiValue from (SELECT DATETIME_ID, 100*SUM(PMMBMSSESSIONESTABSUCC)/SUM(PMMBMSSESSIONESTABATT) AS KPI_Value FROM DC_E_ERBS_MCEFUNCTION_RAW where DATETIME_ID = @DATETIME_ID  AND MOID=@MOID AND  SN=@SN GROUP BY DATETIME_ID ORDER BY DATETIME_ID ASC) A
